{"tid":1771043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奶共 文在寅晤王毅　籲繼續支持朝鮮半島無核化","createTime":"2019-12-05T14:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T17:25:55.000Z","uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf34aec23518f4ec17ee7a647af83c7b06f224b","tid":1771043,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在南韓訪問的國務委員兼外長王毅，與南韓總統文在寅會面時稱，面對單邊主義等威脅，中韓要加強對話合作。<br />\n<br />\n王毅又指，會為文在寅本月到中國出席中日韓三邊會談做好準備，以促進三國合作。<br />\n<br />\n文在寅就表示，朝鮮半島無核化及和平進程正處於重要階段，希望中方繼續推進半島和平進程。<br />\n<br />\n此外有消息指，中韓兩國商議爭取國家主席習近平能早日訪問南韓。中方表示，正認真考慮習近平明年上半年，應邀訪韓一事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=372369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372369&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=c19da149\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372369&h=1ae14d31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=372369</a>"},{"pid":"6e220bd95af04ba2f28db84422ceaed2ed052476","tid":1771043,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eebe3f9f493049b07928c04b8ae22b3bda1b6a4","tid":1771043,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e220bd95af04ba2f28db84422ceaed2ed052476","tid":1771043,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"韓國搞乜鳩....<br />\n無一任總統正常"},{"pid":"1131636e5d58e4590d305641c33e55a760c17588","tid":1771043,"uid":142888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"人哋只係一個小國，仲要同緊日本打貿易戰，你想人哋做咩？"},{"pid":"c877325f99